tice-8411989.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>2015年沃特森因一直拒绝评论被卷入性侵丑闻的前内政大臣{{le|利昂·布里坦|Leon Brittan}}而被批评，布里坦曾写信给{{le|检事总长|Director of Public Prosecutions (England and Wales)}}申诉，警方后来不得不向布里坦的家人道歉，他的家人没有被告知他的案件在他去世前被放弃了。沃特森在他死后坚持指控。<ref>{{Cite news|url = |title = Watson urged to break silence over Lord Brittan abuse claims|trans_title=沃特森敦促打破对布里坦爵士滥用权利的沉默|last = Cecil|first = Nicholas|date = 9 October 2015|work = London Evening Standard|access-date = |via = |page = 6}}</ref>大伦敦警察厅审查了强奸指控，但是警官没有找到充足的证据来采取进一步行动，虽然当时仍在调查关于布里坦的虐待儿童的多项指控。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.sky.com/story/1566864/watson-defends-actions-over-brittan-rape-claims|title=Watson Defends Actions Over Brittan Rape Claims|trans_title=沃特森坚持对布里坦强奸案的行动|author=Tom Parmenter|work=Sky News|accessdate=2017-01-27|archive-date=2016-06-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617001602/http://news.sky.com/story/1566864/watson-defends-actions-over-brittan-rape-claims|dead-url=no}}</ref>

